PRACTICAL-2 

Deploying a React Application on Firebase Hosting

To create a React application, build it for production, and deploy it on Firebase 
Hosting so that it is accessible via a public URL. 


 npx create-react-app my-app 
cd myapp


npm install firebase-tools

firbase login
fibase init
hosting and (optionally) select spacebar+enter

use existing project and select

build

yes

no

npm run build

firebase deploy

open link in other browser or phone


code:

